PN,39301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775056271
OL,3,CMum whose baby has fatal blood
OL,4,Ccondition urges people to join stem
OL,5,Ccell register
OL,7,FA mother is urging people to join the
OL,8,Fstem cell register after her son was
OL,9,Fdiagnosed with a fatal blood condition
OL,10,Fa week before his first birthday.
OL,12,FRonnie, from Merseyside, was diagnosed
OL,13,Fwith aplastic anaemia - which is fatal
OL,14,Fif left untreated - after his mum,
OL,15,FLaura, noticed he was bruising more.
OL,17,FIt happens when the bone marrow cannot
OL,18,Fmake enough new blood cells for the
OL,19,Fbody to work normally, with around 100
OL,20,Fto 150 new cases in the UK every year.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775056271
OL,3,CMum whose baby has fatal blood
OL,4,Ccondition urges people to join stem
OL,5,Ccell register
OL,7,FLaura, 30, said: "He had only just
OL,8,Fstarted crawling, then three days
OL,9,Flater when I got him up, he had blood
OL,10,Fcoming from his nose, blisters in his
OL,11,Fmouth, and red dots on his body."
OL,13,FHe was taken to Alder Hey Children's
OL,14,FHospital in Liverpool for blood and
OL,15,Fplatelet transfusions, after experts
OL,16,Fsuspected he had leukaemia.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775056271
OL,3,CMum whose baby has fatal blood
OL,4,Ccondition urges people to join stem
OL,5,Ccell register
OL,7,FLaura said: "The room went quiet, our
OL,8,Fhearts were pounding, and then
OL,9,Finstantly our minds were jumping to
OL,10,Fthe worst-case scenario and thinking
OL,11,Fhow is my 11-month-old meant to battle
OL,12,Fsuch a deadly disease at such a young
OL,13,Fage.
OL,15,F"This is a day that will forever be
OL,16,Fengraved in our minds, every time we
OL,17,Fhear sirens now it takes us back to
OL,18,Fthat night of being blue lighted to
OL,19,FAlder Hey."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775056271
OL,3,CMum whose baby has fatal blood
OL,4,Ccondition urges people to join stem
OL,5,Ccell register
OL,7,FCancer was later ruled out, although
OL,8,Fdoctors were struggling to test
OL,9,FRonnie's bone marrow as it was so
OL,10,Fsparse.
OL,12,FThe family was told his levels were at
OL,13,F5% with very few cells, when a baby
OL,14,Fhis age should have 100%.
OL,16,FA second test revealed Ronnie had
OL,17,Faplastic anaemia and his parents were
OL,18,Ftold a bone marrow transplant would be
OL,19,Fhis only hope of a cure.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775056271
OL,3,CMum whose baby has fatal blood
OL,4,Ccondition urges people to join stem
OL,5,Ccell register
OL,7,FLaura said her son is still "happy and
OL,8,Fsmiling" despite having infusions and
OL,9,Finjections to stimulate his bone
OL,10,Fmarrow production.
OL,12,FHowever, there is also a worry over
OL,13,Finfections as Ronnie has been
OL,14,Fdiagnosed with neutropenia.
OL,16,FThis causes a type of white blood cell
OL,17,Fthat is essential for fighting
OL,18,Fbacterial infections to become
OL,19,Fabnormally low.
OL,26,@oD@]OUpD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775056271
OL,3,CMum whose baby has fatal blood
OL,4,Ccondition urges people to join stem
OL,5,Ccell register
OL,7,FThe family is working with the charity
OL,8,FAnthony Nolan on the Register4Ronnie
OL,9,Fcampaign.
OL,11,FThey hope this will encourage more
OL,12,Fpeople to join the stem cell register
OL,13,Fto help children like Ronnie, as well
OL,14,Fas youngsters with other conditions
OL,15,Fsuch as leukaemia.
OL,17,FLaura said: "Now we have a diagnosis
OL,18,Fwe have to do something to help."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775056271
OL,3,CMum whose baby has fatal blood
OL,4,Ccondition urges people to join stem
OL,5,Ccell register
OL,7,F"There are so many other kids out
OL,8,Fthere who need a match, we are putting
OL,9,Fit out there for Ronnie and to educate
OL,10,Fpeople about the lifesaving potential
OL,11,Fof stem cell transplants.
OL,13,F"Being from Merseyside, we all stick
OL,14,Ftogether from here.
OL,16,F"We're sharing Ronnie's story because
OL,17,Fwe want people to get tested, if a
OL,18,Fmatch comes up for him then great, but
OL,19,Fa match for someone else, that's
OL,20,Famazing as well."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775056271
OL,3,CMum whose baby has fatal blood
OL,4,Ccondition urges people to join stem
OL,5,Ccell register
OL,7,FAplastic anaemia can affect anyone at
OL,8,Fany age, but is more common in people
OL,9,Faged between 10 and 20, and those over
OL,10,F60.
OL,12,FSymptoms include tiredness, shortness
OL,13,Fof breath, headaches, bleeding from
OL,14,Fthe nose or gums, and infections.
OL,16,FLaura is urging people to join the
OL,17,FAnthony Nolan stem cell register,
OL,18,Fwhich is free and aimed at people aged
OL,19,F16-30.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775056271
OL,3,CMum whose baby has fatal blood
OL,4,Ccondition urges people to join stem
OL,5,Ccell register
OL,7,FHolly Gooch from Anthony Nolan said:
OL,8,F"We need more amazing people to join
OL,9,Fthe stem cell register to save people
OL,10,Fjust like Ronnie.
OL,12,F"We need more young people, especially
OL,13,Fmen, and more people from minority
OL,14,Fethnic backgrounds. We need as much of
OL,15,Fa diverse register as possible so we
OL,16,Fcan give every patient who needs one,
OL,17,Fa second chance at life."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775056271
OL,3,CMum whose baby has fatal blood
OL,4,Ccondition urges people to join stem
OL,5,Ccell register
OL,7,FShe said young people are more likely
OL,8,Fto provide a better outcome for
OL,9,Fpatients, and people are more likely
OL,10,Fto find a match with people of a
OL,11,Fsimilar ethnicity.
OL,13,FHolly said the register desperately
OL,14,Fneeds more young people to join the
OL,15,Fregister, as you become ineligible to
OL,16,Fdonate once you reach 61.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
